query:
UPDATE projects
               SET name = $2,
                   git_repo_path = $3,
                   setup_script = $4,
                   dev_script = $5,
                   cleanup_script = $6,
                   copy_files = $7,
                   has_remote = $8,
                   github_repo_owner = $9,
                   github_repo_name = $10,
                   github_repo_id = $11
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         name,
                         git_repo_path,
                         setup_script,
                         dev_script,
                         cleanup_script,
                         copy_files,
                         has_remote as "has_remote!: bool",
                         github_repo_owner,
                         github_repo_name,
                         github_repo_id,
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
